                            <li class="mb-2">Worked on internal utility tools and public-facing corporate websites.</li>
                            <li>Optimized database queries, implemented caching which resulted in 30% faster page load times.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Education -->
            <section class="mb-5">
                <h3 class="section-heading">Education</h3>
                <div class="card timeline-card">
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-1">
                            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-0">B.S. in Computer Science</h5>
                            <span class="text-muted small">2015 – 2019</span>
